    {
      "id": "natural-writing-en-subagent-default",
      "category": "subagent-default/writing",
      "fixture": "substantive-writing-en-readonly",
      "tools": ["todo", "task", "hub", "read", "grep", "glob"],
      "prompt": "Read the two English LaTeX paragraphs in section.tex and propose a conservative revision that improves their claim-evidence relationship, resolves the ambiguous phrase 'This improvement', and makes the comparison between stopping rules easier to follow. Preserve every qualifier, modality, negation, number, citation, LaTeX command, experimental limitation, and the distinction between observed results and an equal-compute counterfactual. Independently check the complete proposed revision for semantic drift and explain the final wording. Do not modify files or use the network.",
